  }, "v4"), mdx("p", null, "Trong th\xE0nh ch\u1EB3ng c\xF2n th\u1EE9c \u0103n. N\u1EBFu ch\xFAng ta \u0111i v\xE0o th\xE0nh s\u1EBD ch\u1EBFt, m\xE0 ng\u1ED3i \u0111\xE2y th\xEC c\u0169ng ch\u1EBFt. Chi b\u1EB1ng ch\xFAng ta \u0111i \u0111\u1EBFn doanh tr\u1EA1i A-ram. May ra h\u1ECD \u0111\u1EC3 ch\xFAng ta s\u1ED1ng th\xEC t\u1ED1t c\xF2n n\u1EBFu h\u1ECD gi\u1EBFt ch\xFAng ta th\xEC \u0111\u1EB1ng n\xE0o ch\xFAng ta c\u0169ng ch\u1EBFt th\xF4i.\" "), mdx("h6", {
